issue.title: Bug: I noticed that Obsidian was freezing on the trait text.

labels.name: need more info
labels.description: This issue needs more info on it in order to be worked on

issue.body: - [ X ] I have verified that I am on the latest version of the Linter ## Describe the Bug I was using Obsidian and noticed that my app kept freezing. I started by disabling all plugins and found that the freezing was caused by the Linter plugin. I also found that this happened all the time under certain circumstances. ## How to Reproduce Steps to reproduce the behavior: Example to reproduce issue with ``` markdown --- tags: [] title: Bug Reproduce date created: 2023-10-28T02:29:30 date modified: 2023-10-28T02:30:36 --- - Hi. This is a note to reproduce the bug. - There must be at least one bullet point. - Add an empty line and write one or more bullet points again like this. - Then run the linter plugin and the Obsidian app should freeze. ``` ## Expected Behavior In short, your Obsidian app will freeze. ## Device - [x] Desktop: Silicon mac - [ ] Mobile (I haven't tried it on mobile.)

comment.body: Hey @wangyu92 , does this issue still exist for you? I see that the issue is pretty old and has not been updated in a while. I plan on closing this if I do not hear back since I cannot reproduce the issue in question.
